Direct Auto Parts open its doors in 1962 specializing in supplying quality recycled car and truck parts,and has not looked back since. It soon became an industry leader and with such a wide customer base it saw the need for an alternative to factory OEM parts and in 1991 purchased a leading Winnipeg aftermarket jobber parts supplier and opened up a new modern store on wall st in Winnipeg. continually growing in 2002 direct auto purchased Winnipeg engine and trans supplying rebuilt engines and transmissions gives there customers even more options.with the ability to supply recycled,rebuilt and new parts direct auto parts truly is your one stop for all your auto part needs.now with 3 stores to serve you direct auto parts is proud to be a family owned Manitoba based company
